Titolo: Kung Fu Rider

Anno: 2010

Descrizione: Kung Fu Rider (Japanese: 街スベリ, Chinese: 功夫滑仔), previously known as Slider, is an action video game for the PlayStation 3. The game is developed by Japan Studio and published by Sony Computer Entertainment for use with the PlayStation Move controller. It was officially unveiled at the 2010 Game Developers Conference in San Francisco. It was released in Australia on September 16, 2010, in Europe and North America on September 17, and Japan on October 21, and received mostly negative reviews from critics.

